reviewText: This is one of Dr. Wayne Dyer's finest programs on spirituality and experiencing the miraculous. This program opened my mind to new ideas and realities. I highly recommend it.

reviewText: Dr. Dyers presentations are more than I've ever experienced. I'm certain anyone who purchases "Experiencing the Miraculous" will feel being "There"' if ony for a short time, and will happy they made the journey with Wayne Dyer. After all, men of such strong faith come along relatively rarely in a lifetime !

reviewText: After first watching, within five minutes, I was going to "gift" this purchase to someone else because i'm thinking, "he's just standing in a church lecturing, wtf," but after listening to his words and gauging the audience, I started to feel like I was there with him.  For me, the sacredness of the sites was palpable.  I can't wait to experience Lourdes and Assissi first hand.Yes, the production sucks, but if you can get past that - the messages are beautiful, in Wayne Dyer fashion.

reviewText: I bought this from Hay House but will do a review here.  What a disappointment this DVD is.  The audio and video are very poor; one of the guest speakers can't be understood at all and the audience noise is very distracting. There is nothing new here just more of the same from previous works.  I have always been a Wayne Dyer fan but this collection is not worth the money.

reviewText: These 4 DVDs are great.  Dr Dyer is very intertaining and gives good advice.  He is a wonderful speaker and a wonderful human being.  I wish I had been on this tour with him.
